#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:30
msgid "How to Use EPLB"
msgstr "如何使用 EPLB"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:32
msgid "EPLB has three usage modes:"
msgstr "EPLB 有三种使用模式："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "Mode"
msgstr "模式"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "Config in `eplb_config`"
msgstr "`eplb_config` 配置"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "Env Variable"
msgstr "环境变量"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "**Dynamic EPLB**"
msgstr "**动态 EPLB**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "`dynamic_eplb: true`"
msgstr "`dynamic_eplb: true`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "`DYNAMIC_EPLB=true`"
msgstr "`DYNAMIC_EPLB=true`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "**Recording** (generate expert map)"
msgstr "**记录模式** (生成专家映射表)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "`expert_map_record_path`"
msgstr "`expert_map_record_path`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "`DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` or `EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=true`"
msgstr "`DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` 或 `EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=true`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "**Static EPLB** (load pre-recorded map)"
msgstr "**静态 EPLB** (加载预记录映射表)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "`expert_map_path`"
msgstr "`expert_map_path`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "none required"
msgstr "无需设置"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:40
msgid ""
"[!IMPORTANT] For Dynamic EPLB and Recording modes, the env variable acts "
"as a safety guard: setting `dynamic_eplb: true` in config alone is not "
"enough — the assertion requires `DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` or "
"`EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=true`. Static EPLB (loading a pre-recorded map via "
"`expert_map_path`) does **not** require an env variable."
msgstr ""
"[!重要] 对于动态 EPLB 和记录模式，环境变量作为安全防护：仅在配置中设置 `dynamic_eplb: true` 是不够的——断言要求同时设置 "
"`DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` 或 `EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=true`。静态 EPLB（通过 "
"`expert_map_path` 加载预记录映射表）**不**需要设置环境变量。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:43
msgid "Dynamic EPLB"
msgstr "动态 EPLB"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:45
msgid ""
"We need to add environment variable `export DYNAMIC_EPLB=\"true\"` to "
"enable vLLM EPLB. Enable dynamic balancing with auto-tuned parameters. "
"Adjust expert_heat_collection_interval and algorithm_execution_interval "
"based on workload patterns. In the current version, we recommend using "
"the following: policy of swift balancer(2)."
msgstr ""
"需要添加环境变量 `export DYNAMIC_EPLB=\"true\"` 来启用 vLLM 的 EPLB "
"功能。通过自动调优的参数启用动态平衡。根据工作负载模式调整 `expert_heat_collection_interval` 和 "
"`algorithm_execution_interval`。在当前版本中，建议使用以下策略：swift balancer(2)。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:60
msgid "EPLB Policy Types"
msgstr "EPLB 策略类型"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:62
msgid ""
"The `eplb_policy_type` parameter selects the balancing algorithm used "
"during dynamic expert redistribution:"
msgstr "`eplb_policy_type` 参数选择动态专家重分布期间使用的平衡算法："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "Value"
msgstr "值"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "Policy"
msgstr "策略"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "`0`"
msgstr "`0`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "Random"
msgstr "随机"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "Randomly swaps experts between ranks. Suitable for basic testing only."
msgstr "在 ranks 之间随机交换专家。仅适用于基础测试。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "`1`"
msgstr "`1`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "DefaultEplb"
msgstr "DefaultEplb"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid ""
"Open-source EPLB algorithm. Adds redundant experts to the hottest, packs "
"via balanced assignment with local constraint exchange."
msgstr "开源 EPLB 算法。为最热的专家添加冗余，通过平衡分配和局部约束交换进行打包。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "`2`"
msgstr "`2`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "SwiftBalanceEplb"
msgstr "SwiftBalanceEplb"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid ""
"Optimized for low-bandwidth environments. Supports intra-node and inter-"
"node expert redundancy, joint optimization of expert placement. "
"**(Recommended)**"
msgstr "针对低带宽环境优化。支持节点内和节点间专家冗余，联合优化专家放置。**（推荐）**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "`3`"
msgstr "`3`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid "FlashLB"
msgstr "FlashLB"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md
msgid ""
"Statistical method using sliding-window mean/variance/covariance of "
"expert loads. Uses FlashTree layered search for optimal replica "
"allocation and `minimize_redeploy` for incremental adjustment. Best for "
"high-frequency load fluctuations."
msgstr "统计方法，使用专家负载的滑动窗口均值/方差/协方差。使用 FlashTree 分层搜索进行最优副本分配，并使用 `minimize_redeploy` 进行增量调整。最适合高频负载波动场景。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:71
msgid "Static EPLB"
msgstr "静态 EPLB"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:73
msgid "Initial Setup (Record Expert Map)"
msgstr "初始设置（记录专家映射表）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:75
msgid ""
"We need to add environment variable `export EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=\"true\"` "
"to record expert map. Generate the initial expert distribution map using "
"expert_map_record_path. This creates a baseline configuration for future "
"deployments."
msgstr ""
"需要添加环境变量 `export EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=\"true\"` 来记录专家映射表。使用 "
"`expert_map_record_path` 生成初始专家分布图。这为未来的部署创建了基准配置。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:89
msgid "Subsequent Deployments (Use Recorded Map)"
msgstr "后续部署（使用已记录的映射表）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:91
msgid ""
"Load the pre-recorded expert map for consistent performance. This avoids "
"recalculating distributions at runtime."
msgstr "加载预先记录的专家映射表以获得一致的性能。这避免了在运行时重新计算分布。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:102
msgid "Critical Considerations"
msgstr "关键注意事项"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:104
msgid "Parameter Tuning:"
msgstr "参数调优："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:105
msgid ""
"expert_heat_collection_interval: Higher values (e.g., 400+) for stable "
"workloads; lower values (e.g., 100-200) for fluctuating traffic."
msgstr ""
"expert_heat_collection_interval：对于稳定的工作负载，建议使用较高值（如 "
"400+）；对于波动的流量，建议使用较低值（如 100-200）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:106
msgid ""
"algorithm_execution_interval: Should be ≥ 30 to avoid premature balancing"
" during startup."
msgstr "algorithm_execution_interval：应 ≥ 30，以避免在启动阶段过早进行平衡。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:107
msgid ""
"num_redundant_experts: Must match tensor-parallel size (e.g., 16 for 16 "
"NPUs) to ensure sufficient redundancy."
msgstr "num_redundant_experts：必须匹配张量并行 (TP) 大小（例如 16 张 NPU 则设为 16），以确保足够的冗余度。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:109
msgid "Hardware Requirements:"
msgstr "硬件要求："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:110
msgid ""
"Ensure that all NPUs have identical memory capacity and compute "
"capabilities."
msgstr "确保所有 NPU 具有相同的显存容量和计算能力。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:111
msgid ""
"Network bandwidth must support expert redistribution traffic (≥ 10 Gbps "
"recommended)."
msgstr "网络带宽必须支持专家重分布的流量（建议 ≥ 10 Gbps）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:113
msgid "Model Compatibility:"
msgstr "模型兼容性："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:114
msgid ""
"Only MoE models with explicit expert parallelism support (e.g., Qwen3 MoE"
" models) are compatible."
msgstr "仅支持具有显式专家并行支持的 MoE 模型（如 Qwen3 MoE 模型）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:115
msgid ""
"Verify model architecture supports dynamic expert routing through "
"`--enable-expert-parallel`."
msgstr "通过 `--enable-expert-parallel` 验证模型架构是否支持动态专家路由。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:117
msgid "Monitoring & Validation:"
msgstr "监控与验证："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:118
msgid ""
"Track metrics: expert_load_balance_ratio, ttft_p99, tpot_avg, and "
"npu_utilization."
msgstr "跟踪以下指标：expert_load_balance_ratio、ttft_p99、tpot_avg 以及 npu_utilization。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:119
msgid "Use vLLM monitor to detect imbalances during runtime."
msgstr "使用 vLLM monitor 检测运行时的不平衡情况。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:120
msgid ""
"Always verify expert map JSON structure before loading (validate with jq "
"or similar tools)."
msgstr "加载前务必验证专家映射表的 JSON 结构（使用 jq 或类似工具验证）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:122
msgid "Startup Behavior:"
msgstr "启动行为："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:123
msgid ""
"Initial requests may experience higher latency during the first balancing"
" cycle (typically 1-2 minutes)."
msgstr "在第一个平衡周期内（通常为 1-2 分钟），初始请求可能会经历较高的延迟。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:124
msgid "Avoid sudden traffic spikes during the warm-up phase."
msgstr "避免在预热阶段出现突发流量高峰。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:126
msgid "Common Pitfalls:"
msgstr "常见陷阱："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:127
msgid ""
"Incorrect tensor-parallel-size vs. actual NPU count → causes resource "
"underutilization."
msgstr "张量并行大小 (TP size) 与实际 NPU 数量不符 → 导致资源利用不足。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:128
msgid "Using expert_map_path without generating the map first → runtime errors."
msgstr "在未生成映射表的情况下使用 expert_map_path → 导致运行时错误。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/eplb_swift_balancer.md:129
msgid "Setting num_redundant_experts > available NPUs → system failure."
msgstr "设置 num_redundant_experts 大于可用 NPU 数量 → 导致系统故障。"
